class_notes: EMPH Students Only; Outside permission to enroll in course must be approved by EMPH leadership. EMPH Opening Weekend is January 13-15 and Closing Weekend is April 14-16
course_description: Course focuses on the theory & application of qualitative data analysis from multiple sources, including focus group & interview data. Students will use MaxQDA software to analyze previously collected data samples.
prerequisites: PRS 532D and PRS 535D as prerequisites or special permission required to enroll.
